(c) Medical education, liaison, and any Phase IV Clinical Trials, within the bounds of this Agreement;
(d) All customer service, product supply, billing, and sales-related activities;
(e) All post-clearance regulatory activities, including those necessary to uphold Regulatory Approvals, as well as actions required to address any updates or modifications to these approvals.
